Package com.enjin.sdk.graphql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphQLVariableHolder<T>
    A interface for GraphQL builders to set variables within them.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GraphQLError
    A class that models the structure of a GraphQL response error.
    GraphQLObjectSerializer
    A class for serializing objects in a GraphQL format.
    GraphQLProcessor
    Singleton class, loads and manages GraphQL template files used by various service classes.
    GraphQLQueryRegistry
    Class for registering and storing GraphQL templates.
    GraphQLRequest<T extends GraphQLRequest<T>>
    Represents a model of a GraphQL request and facilitates the serialization of the query.
    GraphQLRequestBody
    Represents a model of a GraphQL request's body.
    GraphQLResponse<T>
    Models the body of a GraphQLResponse.
    TemplateConstants
